    title: 'End-to-End Encrypted',
    description: 'Every message is encrypted so only you and your recipients can read it. Not even the server can see your conversations.',
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path d="M234.42,111.07l-46.52-30.15A8,8,0,0,0,176,87.72V128a8,8,0,0,0,11.9,6.93l46.52-30.15A4,4,0,0,0,234.42,111.07ZM213.65,124,184,105.34v37.32ZM128,56C81.07,56,28.15,80.68,28.15,128S81.07,200,128,200c17.77,0,34.53-4.67,48.42-13.5a8,8,0,1,0-8.84-13.33C156,180.39,142.23,184,128,184c-39.42,0-83.85-20.59-83.85-56S88.58,72,128,72s83.85,20.59,83.85,56a55.84,55.84,0,0,1-3.34,18.88,8,8,0,1,0,15,5.56A71.85,71.85,0,0,0,227.85,128C227.85,80.68,174.93,56,128,56Zm0,112a40,40,0,0,0,10.77-1.47,8,8,0,0,0-4.32-15.4A24,24,0,1,1,128,104a23.76,23.76,0,0,1,17,7.05,8,8,0,1,0,11.31-11.31A39.8,39.8,0,0,0,128,88,40,40,0,0,0,128,168Z"/></svg>`,
